                        <h2 class="section__title dedicated__title">Privacy Policy</h2>
                        <p>TravelKeys.com is maintained by Travel Keys, a private company. Travel Keys handles matters of privacy with great care. Protecting the confidentiality of our clients and homeowners is a top priority. Personal information is gathered and maintained by Travel Keys for the purposes of contact and billing. The following policy explains the types of information collected, its use and protection.</p>
                        <h2 class="section__title dedicated__title">Collected Information</h2>
                        <p>Travel Keys collects two types of information from our guests and potential clients. TravelKeys.com users may have web-browsing information collected. Non-personal data; such as 'favorites' lists, preferences, page views, and session information, is gathered in an attempt to better improve our user experience and provide increased services to returning site guests. Personal information; such as email addresses, telephone numbers, billing/shipping addresses and credit card information is required to proceed with confirmed vacation rentals. Travel Keys does not require that site browsers provide any personal information.</p>
                        <h2 class="section__title dedicated__title">Collected Information Usage</h2>
                        <p>Non-personal data collected by Travel Keys will be used by the company to better interpret and enhance user experience on our network of websites. Personal data collected by Travel Keys will be used by properly designated personnel for the express purposes of contacting potential guests regarding villa rental requests placed online or over the telephone, contacting existing guests regarding arrival procedures or billing inquiries, confirming selected concierge services with guests and suppliers.<br></p>
                        <h2 class="section__title dedicated__title">Sharing Information</h2>
                        <p>Travel Keys does not sell or rent any of our guest’s personal information to anyone for any reason. Travel Keys will provide personal information to selected/authorized service providers, only in compliance with our guest’s requests. Travel Keys does reserve the right to disclose information as required by law if/when the company believes that disclosure is necessary to protect our rights and/or to comply with a judicial proceeding or court order.</p>
                        <h2 class="section__title dedicated__title">Information Protection</h2>
                        <p>Travel Keys highly values our client’s privacy; we have appropriate security measures in place for all electronically collected personal and non-personal data. Additional precautions have been taken to protect all data against loss, misuse, alteration or distribution.</p>
                        <h2 class="section__title dedicated__title">Information Updates</h2>
                        <p>Travel Keys offers our clients the ability to correct any inaccuracies from gathered personal information. Clients can update/correct personal information by contacting Travel Keys via email or writing to the U.S. mailing address. Those wishing to opt out of receiving Travel Keys communications in the future must let us know by clicking on the "unsubscribe" link within any general communication received. Please allow up to six weeks for the suppression of your contact information.</p>
                        <h2 class="section__title dedicated__title">External Sites</h2>
                        <p>TravelKeys.com and other affiliated network sites provide links to external websites that are not maintained by Travel Keys. Users accessing information linking to outside websites are subject to the privacy policy of these external sites.</p>
                        <p>Have questions or inquiries regarding your personal data?<br> Please <a href="http://www.travelkeys.com/contact-us" title="Contact us">contact</a> Travel Keys.</p>
                    </div>
